definition: classifier for gifts, newspaper, magazine, papers, reports, contracts etc/variant of 分[fen4]

sentences.english: The results appear in July's Archives of Pediatrics &Adolescent Medicine.
sentences.chinese: 研究結果顯示在七月份的青少兒醫學檔案庫裏。

sentences.english: The wall oozed in July there.
sentences.chinese: 那裏的七月份牆面都滲水。

sentences.english: The first of the two films is scheduled to be released in July in select territories.
sentences.chinese: 上集預定七月份在選定的城市上映。

sentences.english: He told me that he (_wolud have been teaching_) here for ten years by July. (teach)
sentences.chinese: 他告訴我到七月份，他在這兒任教將滿十年了。

sentences.english: His concert will being in July.
sentences.chinese: 他的演唱將在七月份開始。

sentences.english: Car sales, for instance, fell to a nine-year low in July.
sentences.chinese: 例如七月份的汽車銷售量下跌到九年最低點。

sentences.english: The arrival punctuality of Finnair flights in July was 79% (85.7%).
sentences.chinese: 芬航航班在七月份的準點率爲79%。

sentences.english: We have penciled in a meeting for July in Shanghai.
sentences.chinese: 我們已經暫定七月份在上海開會。

sentences.english: The July maximum (ie the highest temperature recorded in July) was 30C.
Gass charges will rise in July.
sentences.chinese: 汽油收費在七月份會上漲。

sentences.english: For our complete July averages poll of forecasters, see here.
sentences.chinese: 七月份完整的預測者調查平均結果，請看這裏。

sentences.english: Maybe she gets her baby in July, during World Cup.
sentences.chinese: 或許七月份她就會生產，就在世界盃期間。

sentences.english: When you come again in July, they will have moved into a new house.
sentences.chinese: 七月份你們再來時，他們就搬進新房子裏去了。

sentences.english: He told me that he (_would have_been teaching_) here for ten years by July. (teach)
sentences.chinese: 他告訴我到七月份，他在這兒任教將滿十年了。

sentences.english: The output of July in our factory increased by 25% compared with that of January.
sentences.chinese: 我廠七月份的產量比元月份增加百分之二十五。
